{"tid":411462,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"萬能既連登仔有無人解釋到呢個現象","createTime":"2017-09-23T20:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T06:41:10.000Z","uid":58358,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c22aff6a04c0c66de4afd3cc5a35d15f9dbf9db","tid":411462,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:09:53.000Z","msg":"光有波動 (wave) 既特性<br />\n一串光束射向雙濾間片 (double slit filter) 會產生明暗相間既干擾紋 (interference pattern) 同水波一樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.stack.imgur.com/QKoqU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.stack.imgur.com%2FQKoqU.png&h=1181e706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n光亦有粒子特性 (particle)<br />\n一粒光子 (photon) 即係一個單位能量既載體 (energy packet)<br />\n<br />\n理論上，如果將一粒光子射向是但一條濾間，佢會穿過濾間落係塊幕上面<br />\n如果一粒粒咁射，經過一段時間，有啲撞左落濾片，有啲穿過其中一間，幕上就會顯示兩道平衡既紋<br />\n<br />\n但實驗結果係，幕上顯示既依然係干擾紋<br />\n然而逐粒咁放，已經排除左波動干擾既可能性<br />\n<br />\n呢個現象未有人解釋到<br />\n解釋到呢個現象既人好有可能拎諾貝爾獎"},{"pid":"3984224a844ff7ea11ca87a6a7695814232adb48","tid":411462,"uid":80461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:14:39.000Z","msg":"年經"},{"pid":"07b980275fab76b3a8c8c31bc1553910b450110b","tid":411462,"uid":138752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T21:44:58.000Z","msg":"所以咪有波粒二象性呢個理論出現囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2750f786763e658465cc1bc0427edd86b5d78203","tid":411462,"uid":79471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T22:16:39.000Z","msg":"升中五了"},{"pid":"37a91c21b6d90a7d3e24042bfc7258254e76ca89","tid":411462,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T01:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n但實驗結果係，幕上顯示既依然係干擾紋<br />\n然而逐粒咁放，已經排除左波動干擾既可能性<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://plus.maths.org/content/sites/plus.maths.org/files/articles/2017/contextuality/electrons2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplus.maths.org%2Fcontent%2Fsites%2Fplus.maths.org%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F2017%2Fcontextuality%2Felectrons2.jpg&h=f49532dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"522113f1a5c43bc067dd2f5f7eb0b6efba0f7e24","tid":411462,"uid":35317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T01:29:46.000Z","msg":"愛因斯坦100年前咪解釋左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc355ee0fe5ab0f52e4f8b7d596322464d17218","tid":411462,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T01:33:24.000Z","msg":"然後啲人想知究竟粒子係穿過邊一條間去到另一邊，於是就加左探測器，重覆實驗<br />\n<br />\n但結果顯示，當你追蹤每個粒子既時候，佢地既落點形成兩條間，並非之前既干擾紋<br />\n<img src=\"http://genesismission.4t.com/Physics/Quantum_Mechanics/slit/Two-Slit_Experiment_Particles_watched.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgenesismission.4t.com%2FPhysics%2FQuantum_Mechanics%2Fslit%2FTwo-Slit_Experiment_Particles_watched.gif&h=432fd99c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b094e9cb3c1a37b68a3a4fa9147f849ebb18f4df","tid":411462,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T01:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/z5agmdrl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz5agmdrl&h=7c61e6c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"638f98d9529d01c75ccc82e8a01e7754b4db260a","tid":411462,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T01:37:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>然後啲人想知究竟粒子係穿過邊一條間去到另一邊，於是就加左探測器，重覆實驗<br />\n<br />\n但結果顯示，當你追蹤每個粒子既時候，佢地既落點形成兩條間，並非之前既干擾紋<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2itd0aze\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2itd0aze&h=84ad65fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"793dd280ab36cb66cfb013c28d7835edec68a033","tid":411462,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T01:41:11.000Z","msg":"然後啲人就試下關閉探測器電源，再重覆實驗，結果係干擾紋又再出現<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/z5agmdrl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz5agmdrl&h=7c61e6c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c9c748c0a6045761fac233ddcbdf9895fba1cae","tid":411462,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T01:46:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n但實驗結果係，幕上顯示既依然係干擾紋<br />\n然而逐粒咁放，已經排除左波動干擾既可能性<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://plus.maths.org/content/sites/plus.maths.org/files/articles/2017/contextuality/electrons2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplus.maths.org%2Fcontent%2Fsites%2Fplus.maths.org%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F2017%2Fcontextuality%2Felectrons2.jpg&h=f49532dc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n係每粒particle經過時 自己同自己 interfere<br />\n如果用日常語言就係嗰粒particle同穿過兩個slit"},{"pid":"e65c386b391a17ee7bf30c09ac5d9b1c1c28545f","tid":411462,"uid":60166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T01:52:48.000Z","msg":"有咩解釋唔到？"},{"pid":"2803dcc07efe50313cda854b312db6395cbb3cd7","tid":411462,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T02:03:18.000Z","msg":"以上實驗得出既結論係: 粒子會根據一條概率方程 (probability function) 去到另一邊，干擾紋其實就係概率既描述<br />\n<br />\n係一個粒子未到達瑩幕前，佢可以係處於任何一點，直至觀察者搵到佢，observation collapses probability function. <br />\n<br />\n所以如果係濾間前加上探測器，就等於改變左概率方程: 由於粒子知到自己早就被發現，所以就索性跟住條 path 去另一邊<br />\n<br />\n但問題係，點解粒子會有呢個行為？<br />\n呢個問題困擾左人類好多年，甚至有人消極咁認為根本唔應該問點解"},{"pid":"ec0789fc482a02bdcd1ba4598b9c00002a452f60","tid":411462,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T02:10:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>升中五了</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a16eda5f978e7b4c91230c6ee82337188cff0f35","tid":411462,"uid":31237,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T02:11:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以上實驗得出既結論係: 粒子會根據一條概率方程 (probability function) 去到另一邊，干擾紋其實就係概率既描述<br />\n<br />\n係一個粒子未到達瑩幕前，佢可以係處於任何一點，直至觀察者搵到佢，observation collapses probability function. <br />\n<br />\n所以如果係濾間前加上探測器，就等於改變左概率方程: 由於粒子知到自己早就被發現，所以就索性跟住條 path 去另一邊<br />\n<br />\n但問題係，點解粒子會有呢個行為？<br />\n呢個問題困擾左人類好多年，甚至有人消極咁認為根本唔應該問點解</blockquote><br />\n科學唔係去解釋啲野點解係咁<br />\n物理公式係描述依個世界點運作<br />\n如果問依個世界係點解係咁運作就變左哲學問題"},{"pid":"081866bc63ffaefb1c83beb1a6bbdf9f777f57e9","tid":411462,"uid":38691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T02:15:07.000Z","msg":"邊撚個同你講未解釋到？"},{"pid":"e7da5ef865a961da95d7fb7776e36e7535675eb9","tid":411462,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T02:50:04.000Z","msg":"樓主擺明係想用講故事既形式去講quantum，點解硬係有人走出黎叻唔切<br />\n睇完第一post唔明係正常，但係睇到樓主覆既第二第三個comment都唔明既話真係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928335b00658a1f65cc3b33d425bce7ee8988fb8","tid":411462,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:58:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主擺明係想用講故事既形式去講quantum，點解硬係有人走出黎叻唔切<br />\n睇完第一post唔明係正常，但係睇到樓主覆既第二第三個comment都唔明既話真係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nClickbite title <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05771dcbf9e0cba6ccd8bffe28d8f087d5c5b05","tid":411462,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:58:47.000Z","msg":"我想問逐粒射既實驗係真空做會唔會有影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26322b5bcd7ea8ecfbb46338c7ddd7340e761b5","tid":411462,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T06:41:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想問逐粒射既實驗係真空做會唔會有影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n實驗一定係真空做<br />\n否則就會撞到空氣粒子 (air molecules)"}]}